summary: A custom ENB with horror inspired nights and hard-lighted days.
descriptionHtml:
[size=3]Intensity ENB[/size]

This mod creates a unique graphical effect in Skyrim by increasing certain lighting ppoperties in the base ENB.

The days have hard shadows and intense lighting. At evening a reddish cast comes over the sky and land. At night, vibrant colors emerge in the night sky.

-This uses Boris Vorontsoz\'s ENB series graphics mod.
author: Pocoloon-Bulljump
